{"tid":2430595,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"葛民輝失業2年零收入　沒炒掉1個員工「你忍心他們走？」","createTime":"2021-03-03T04:55:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T06:57:26.000Z","uid":212249,"like":33,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c2dab1d64e24de9b8c4c399a2e864e6b4f144fb1","tid":2430595,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T04:55:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/XPtxw715O0knja19CKyAdSfegqo=/640x397/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VZADEZ5PYNEZRFBHNUXFLXMPX4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FXPtxw715O0knja19CKyAdSfegqo%3D%2F640x397%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVZADEZ5PYNEZRFBHNUXFLXMPX4.jpg&h=151c3931&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n54歲香港諧星葛民輝除了拍戲，也是香港潮流界的代表人物，本身亦自創潮流服裝品牌4A及工作室，然而近兩年受到香港歷經反送中運動及武漢肺炎疫情，連帶影響他的事業。日前，葛民輝接拍好友劉翁執導的鬼片《糖街製片廠》，雖然戲份不多，但總算接到片約。他談到過去兩年的不景氣，坦承身為老板也手足無措。<br />\n<br />\n據香港《壹週刊》報導，葛民輝道出真實情況，「以往大家都習慣中秋有工作，聖誕又有其他工作，會有個周期性。但突然周期性不見了。從社會運動（反送中）開始最近幾年，拍戲、廣告、推廣等等都停頓，我們失業接近兩年」。葛民輝承認一般老板心態都是一動不如一靜，但他從沒想過用裁員來解決問題，坦承「每個月都要照顧他們」。<br />\n<br />\n葛民輝說：「外面風大雨大，你忍心真叫他們(員工)走？不可能啦，你見到個世界環境是怎麼樣。這兩年全世界都停頓了，但可以拚命一起捱過，我們向來關係都好像一家人一樣。」葛民輝多年來把員工當家人照顧，他感性說到：「以前六、七十年代老板比較有人情味，知道員工女兒開始讀書，都會為他著想。以前的老板會希望你安心工作，幫你解決家裡問題，安居樂業。好像一家人，過年都會一起吃飯，有福同享。後來不知怎麼變成這樣，想辦法榨取大家。」（娛樂中心／綜合報導）"},{"pid":"81a50271fd835f8caa78d0c98c3a9cfec573b58f","tid":2430595,"uid":212249,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T04:55:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210303/CBGGEUQPBVDB7JLBVJLE4IH6RA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210303%2FCBGGEUQPBVDB7JLBVJLE4IH6RA%2F&d=uMWHtpimsJ%2FyHBgDjrBiuhq8xf71D2STVxQEH8iwqLk%3D&h=8e0406e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210303%2FCBGGEUQPBVDB7JLBVJLE4IH6RA%2F&h=9af18ebc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210303/CBGGEUQPBVDB7JLBVJLE4IH6RA/</a>"},{"pid":"b2bcda03d8389f0293cf05a440b069ac627eb516","tid":2430595,"uid":90660,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T04:55:55.000Z","msg":"respect"},{"pid":"796e9b61d039f838601a81c65a3f9fbc5d2a7b2d","tid":2430595,"uid":4826,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T04:56:20.000Z","msg":"冇炒但有冇出糧?"},{"pid":"c041a23b60f30eefaf2a5a8bcf1c5c41cad613fb","tid":2430595,"uid":188810,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T04:59:19.000Z","msg":"其實賠足錢我覺得冇拖冇欠<br />\n我作為打工仔都接受<br />\n<br />\n唔明點解近年傳媒咁多呢類煽情報導"},{"pid":"347136948d51feb8b7417cfcb6c338ea37bce1dc","tid":2430595,"uid":211461,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T05:05:21.000Z","msg":"2000幾年之前孟子都已經講咗<br />\n你點對人 人點對你"},{"pid":"e586c5f5ed493c858eb860727d1b1be841575c20","tid":2430595,"uid":85190,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T05:10:43.000Z","msg":"從社會運動（反送中）開始最近幾年，拍戲、廣告、推廣等等都停頓<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f724942962b4c35cb05232ae7a1d28a0c50be6b","tid":2430595,"uid":14422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T05:17:00.000Z","msg":"佢宜家仲同何韻詩拍youtube"},{"pid":"e4a4b3ad8894ef1ad075b528f84570fe157d5f2d","tid":2430595,"uid":37413,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T05:23:05.000Z","msg":"佢商台有開咪嘅，唔算零收入"},{"pid":"7cd1025c9b4e6548e54c6bb77d46176038a027ea","tid":2430595,"uid":2772,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"e586c5f5ed493c858eb860727d1b1be841575c20","tid":243059